 wang kareem roe and matthew bartlett paul hastings is a leading global law firm with a strong presence throughout asia europe latin america and the united states through a collaborative approach entrepreneurial spirit and commitment to client service the professionals of paul hastings deliver innovative solutions to many of the world’s top financial institutions and fortune  companies previous filtration group acquires essentra’s porous technologies business  next cdh investments sells us million stake in wh group  previous bcd acquisition inc to acquire american trailer works inc  next teleperformance to acquire languageline solutions for  billion  previous financing for proposed acquisition of iconic pinewood studios  next samsung electronics america to acquire dacor as an expansion to home appliance portfolio  previous china cosco shipping completes phase i acquisition of piraeus port in greece  next china everbright’s disposal of  share capital of everbright securities international limited  previous jpmorgan leads  billion financing for murphy oil  next garrison sells premier to redwood  previous barclays provides committed financing for acquisition of aetna and humana assets by molina healthcare inc  next paul hastings advises on zobee restructuring  previous junfun investment’s acquisition of majority shareholding of grand concord international  next compass diversified holdings acquires  tactical®  previous gs engineering  construction issues m convertible bonds  next china everbright issues m panda bonds  previous carey watermark investors  acquires san diego marriott la jolla  next paul hastings advises on trinidad power plant financing  previous crédito real sab de cv sofom er completes cash tender offer for senior notes and related consent solicitation  next ip boom continues at paul hastings with life sciences and technology partner addition  previous invesco sells hotel portfolio  next credito real sab de cv announces senior notes offering  previous g