rbridgecom centerbridge partners is a multistrategy private investment firm focused on leveraged buyouts and distressed securities the firm manages over  billion of assets and is based in new york city with an additional office in london the firm invests in both control private equity and public debt with a loantoown strategy and noncontrol public market debt public market equities and other publicly traded securities opportunities the firm  was founded in  by jeffrey aronson and mark gallogly aronson had previously been the head of distressed securities and had founded the leveraged loan business at angelo gordon  co which he had joined in  from lf rothschild  co gallogly was formerly a senior managing director and head of private equity investments at the blackstone group from  until his departure at blackstone gallogly was heavily involved in the firms investments in new skies satellites and sirius satellite radio among others and had joined the firm in  from manufacturers hanover trust company where he worked in acquisition finance in september  the firm raised its debut fund with  billion of investor commitments to focus on control investments in distressed securities as well as leveraged buyout transactions the firm also raised a  billion noncontrol activistoriented credit trading fund known as centerbridge special credit partners through  and  in  the firm announced plans to begin marketing a second investment fund with a target of  billion of investor commitments in  the firm closed its second flagship fund centerbridge partners ii on  billion including a commitment from the gp this was followed by a closing of its bn second special credit partners fund in march  in  centerbridge won control of extended stay hotels a company that gallogly had been involved with at blackstone on  september  centerbridge capital partners announced acquisition of gmac commercial finance a subsidiary of ally financial in  centerbridge acquired p f changs china bistro a chain of 